# Files Tauri's dev watcher should NOT trigger a rebuild for. Without
# this, anything written to src-tauri/ during dev (SQLite WAL/SHM, logs,
# stray .db files) restarts the whole app — see the rebuild loop bug.
# Keep this in sync with `.env` STORAGE_PATH so user data never lives
# inside the watched directory.

*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.log
data/
storage/
